{"data":[{"date":"16:11 28/06","title":"C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 khi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed theo c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 r\u1eddi Nga v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eb5n v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ghi 1 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n, Die Mannschaft c\u00f2n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u00ea ch\u1ec1 r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span>, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; backgrou