u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/155635-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&quot;H\u1ecd ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng thua ch\u1ed5ng v\u00f3 nh\u01b0 b\u1ecdn \u0110\u1ee9c&quot;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 11\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&quot;Hey Brazil, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 b\u1ecf gi\u1ea3i&quot;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/giup-thoat-hiem-o-vong-bang-nguoi-han-duoc-cdv-mexico-xung-thanh-421-189838.html\">Gi\u00fap tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c C\u0110V Mexico&hellip; x\u01b0ng th\u00e1nh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup-421-189834.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nhuc-nha-roi-world-cup-ca-the-gioi-noi-gi-421-189837.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi World Cup, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\">Video: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"685","checkdouble":"189850"},{"date":"16:21 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i cho tr\u1eadn \u201ct\u1eed chi\u1ebfn\u201d Colombia vs Senegal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-senegal-va-du-doan-soi-keo-senegal-vs-colombia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Colombia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Senegal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng </strong>(t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Colombia th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Colombia vs Senegal<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>1h ng\u00e0y 28/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Samara Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Colombia 0.83*0:1/2*-0.88 Senegal<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.94*2 1/2*0.87 \u00cdt<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Senegal v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Senegal v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-senegal-va-du-doan-soi-keo-senegal-vs-colombia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Senegal 21h ng\u00e0y 28/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean BXH l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Colombia (3 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u01a1i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Senegal (4 \u0111i\u1ec3m). Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Senegal n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ngay tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Ba Lan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Senegal, Colombia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1eeda n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 mong r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3? H\u1ecd th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac ngoi sao tan cong cua Colombia co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Colombia m\u1edbi th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng Ba Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Colombia h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111am m\u00ea th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 m\u00e0 Los Cafeteros mang t\u1edbi, ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng d\u00e2ng cao tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nColombia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft trong tay. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Senegal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Koulibaly tin Senegal se vuot qua vong bang\" title=\"Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Kalidou-Koulibaly-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Senegal l\u1ea1i c\u1ee5t h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nColombia t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Senegal. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. Ch\u1ec9 sau 4 ph\u00fat, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi Carlos Sanchez nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2 d\u00f9 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngang ng\u1eeda.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Colombia, xem ra Senegal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft mong \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111ang h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> Colombia th\u1eafng (-1/2)<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Colombia \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i sinh v\u00e0 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan. Nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Juan Cuadrado l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRodriguez c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Juan Quintero v\u00e0 Cuadrado \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho trung phong Radamel Falcao. Ba Lan trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 khi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Los Cafeteros.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Radamel Falcao ghi ban nhan doi cach biet cho DT Colombia.\" title=\"Radamel Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/041506-982959746.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSenegal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t cho ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn Colombia. S\u1ebd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u00e1c ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 Nam M\u1ef9. Rodriguez, Quintero c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng, Cuadrado gi\u1ecfi qu\u1ea5y r\u1ed1i c\u00f2n Falcao nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, Senegal c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ea3 2. N\u1ebfu \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga\u201d c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, gi\u1edd n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Link xem truc tiep Colombia vs Senegal\" title=\"Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Colombia vs Senegal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/link-xem-colombia-vs-senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Senegal l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sadio Mane (Liverpool), v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Mame Biram Diouf, Moussa Konate, M'Baye Niang, Keita Balde, Diafra Sakho\u2026 T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u201cnh\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1n\u201d n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n11 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Senegal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi HLV Aliou Cisse s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng xua qu\u00e2n lao l\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh ra so \u0111\u1ecd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Senegal. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 21h t\u1ed1i nay h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (O 2 1/2)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Colombia th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Colombia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-1 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Colombia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 (-3/4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2 (O 1 1/2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"684","checkdouble":"189851"},{"date":"16:19 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng n\u1eef C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-nu-cdv-bong-da-quyen-ru-nhat-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.\r\n</h2><h2>C\u00e1i d\u1edbp n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 'n\u1ea5m m\u1ed3' ch\u00f4n h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfn binh \u0110\u1ee9c tinh nhu\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0 h\u1ea7u trong chi\u1ebfn tranh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ee9 hai. Khi \u1ea5y, tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 h\u01a1n 70 n\u0103m sau cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn t\u00e0n kh\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 h\u1eadu du\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng 'v\u00f9i m\u00ecnh' tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn d\u01b0\u1edbi tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, nh\u01b0ng chung cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong chuy\u1ebfn sang n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i trong cay \u0111\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/DT-Duc-bai-tran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111ang \u1edf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Song khi m\u00e0 Joachim Loew v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 t\u1eebng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang Confederation Cup v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebb tre. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i khi cho\u00e0ng t\u1ec9nh, Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00dd v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">80 n\u0103m sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 1938, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i \u00f4 nh\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd &rdquo;Die Mannschaft&rdquo; s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006, \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft EURO 2008, b\u00e1n k\u1ebft EURO 2012, \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2010 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014. Song \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ee5t l\u00f9i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eeb EURO 2016.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1.&nbsp;Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y 'nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng' \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Loew\" title=\"HLV Loew\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/huyen-thoai-chi-trich-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-nhuc-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Joachim Loew b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Die Mannschaft t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eabn s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Mats Hummels, Jerome Boateng, Antonio Rudiger hay Niklas Sule, tuy nhi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Joachim Loew \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 b\u00e1o t\u1edbi s\u1edbm v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc-421-189862.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc-421-189862.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f3c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a? H\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft&nbsp;sau 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00ed v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau \u0111\u1ed1ng tro t\u00e0n. V\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-421-189799.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-421-189799.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u1ef1 World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"683","checkdouble":"189852"},{"date":"16:37 28/06","title":"Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/phan-ung-trai-chieu-cua-cdv-duc-vs-han-quoc-sau-tran-cau-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00f3m C\u0110V x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xa t\u1edbi Kazan, Nga ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0.</h2><div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/28/han-quoc.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u1edf Berlin, h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn fan \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/28/duc.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i b\u00ean l\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sao-han-tung-bung-mung-chien-thang-kho-tin-truoc-duc-188-189857.html\">Sao H\u00e0n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc-421-189850.html\">C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\">Video: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dan-anh-ha-he-sau-that-bai-e-che-cua-tuyen-duc-421-189839.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nhuc-nha-roi-world-cup-ca-the-gioi-noi-gi-421-189837.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi World Cup, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup-421-189834.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"682","checkdouble":"189855"},{"date":"16:46 28/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/sao-han-tung-bung-mung-chien-thang-kho-tin-truoc-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Park Shin Hye, Hwang Seung Eun v\u1ee1 \u00f2a khi tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eafng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hinh-anh-sao-Han-mung-chien-thang-Han-Quoc-2-0-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Bae Ki Sung v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat h\u1ed3i h\u1ed9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi khi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i 27/6. Tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, anh vi\u1ebft \"Win\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hwang-Seung-Eun-7841-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Hwang Seung Eun tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c\". Hwang Seung Eun cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4 v\u1ee1 \u00f2a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \"h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, bi\u1ebft \u01a1n\" c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/haha-9199-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean, ca s\u0129 Haha chia s\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 k\u00e8m bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng  \"b\u1eafn tim\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoona-4258-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Yoona \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh to\u00e0n  \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.\u00a0C\u00f4 vi\u1ebft: \"C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\u00a0th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3  l\u00e0m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh\". </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled-5-9634-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ji Sook \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, k\u00e8m theo chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00f3c\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/lee-su-bin-6850-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Lee Su Bin vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram: \"G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c anh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/park-shin-hye-5037-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Park Shin Hye vi\u1ebft: \"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u01a1i. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/jung-hae-in-2554-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0\"Trai \u0111\u1eb9p\" Jung Hae In: \"T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c anh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/sao-1-4115-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Jo Kwon: \"C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoon-3791-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Yoon Kyun Sang: \"\"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 tu\u00f4n r\u01a1i. D\u00f9 cho c\u00e1c anh kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c - m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang ta chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 - c\u00e1c anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh n\u1eefa. K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u, quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Rain-7255-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Rain, \u00f4ng x\u00e3 c\u1ee7a Kim Tae Hee: \"Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. R\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/phan-ung-trai-chieu-cua-cdv-duc-vs-han-quoc-sau-tran-cau-lich-su-461-189855.html\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc-421-189850.html\">C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\">Video: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dan-anh-ha-he-sau-that-bai-e-che-cua-tuyen-duc-421-189839.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nhuc-nha-roi-world-cup-ca-the-gioi-noi-gi-421-189837.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi World Cup, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup-421-189834.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"681","checkdouble":"189857"},{"date":"16:48 28/06","title":"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm: B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.\r\n</h2><h2>C\u00e1i d\u1edbp n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 'n\u1ea5m m\u1ed3' ch\u00f4n h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfn binh \u0110\u1ee9c tinh nhu\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0 h\u1ea7u trong chi\u1ebfn tranh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ee9 hai. Khi \u1ea5y, tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 h\u01a1n 70 n\u0103m sau cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn t\u00e0n kh\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 h\u1eadu du\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng 'v\u00f9i m\u00ecnh' tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn d\u01b0\u1edbi tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, nh\u01b0ng chung cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong chuy\u1ebfn sang n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i trong cay \u0111\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/DT-Duc-bai-tran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111ang \u1edf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Song khi m\u00e0 Joachim Loew v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 t\u1eebng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang Confederation Cup v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebb tre. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i khi cho\u00e0ng t\u1ec9nh, Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00dd v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">80 n\u0103m sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 1938, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i \u00f4 nh\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd &rdquo;Die Mannschaft&rdquo; s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006, \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft EURO 2008, b\u00e1n k\u1ebft EURO 2012, \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2010 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014. Song \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ee5t l\u00f9i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eeb EURO 2016.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1.&nbsp;Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y 'nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng' \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Loew\" title=\"HLV Loew\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/huyen-thoai-chi-trich-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-nhuc-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Joachim Loew b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Die Mannschaft t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eabn s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Mats Hummels, Jerome Boateng, Antonio Rudiger hay Niklas Sule, tuy nhi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Joachim Loew \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 b\u00e1o t\u1edbi s\u1edbm v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc-421-189862.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc-421-189862.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f3c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a? H\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft&nbsp;sau 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00ed v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau \u0111\u1ed1ng tro t\u00e0n. V\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-421-189799.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-421-189799.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u1ef1 World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"680","checkdouble":"189858"},{"date":"17:11 28/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-han-quoc-20-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Cho Hyun-woo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCho Hyun-woo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n trong khung g\u1ed7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Du-am-Han-Quoc-vs-Duc-bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cho Hyun-woo c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Cho Hyun-woo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mario Gomez.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Cho Hyun-woo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 13 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ee9u thua nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Daegu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Leon Goretzka</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Leon Goretzka \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Schalke kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leon Goretzka khong the hien duoc gi nhieu\" title=\"Leon Goretzka kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/got.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leon Goretzka kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.&nbsp;Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 31 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch 1 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf ph\u00fat 62. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Low tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Son Heung-min</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, Son Heung-min kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min ghi ban an dinh chien thang 2-0 cho Han Quoc\" title=\"Son Heung-min ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/son.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Son Heung-min ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSon Heung-min l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n, anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi pha t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, song Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ngay c\u1ea3 trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Manuel Neuer</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Manuel Neuer tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb tay Marc-Andre Ter Stegen. Tuy nhi\u00ean, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Manuel Neuer co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Manuel Neuer c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thu-mon-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Manuel Neuer c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Neuer ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng b\u1eadt ra sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ebd ra Neuer c\u1ea7n b\u0103ng ra s\u1edbm h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p g\u00f3c s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Kim Young-gwon, song anh l\u1ea1i x\u1eed l\u00fd qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 Manuel Neuer b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 4 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong 5 VCK g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (Ph\u00e1p 2002, Italia 2010, T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2014).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 h\u1ecd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Neuer l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mexico</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng F di\u1ec5n ra, v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng Chicharito v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Mexico thua Thuy Dien va chi co the di tiep nho vao ket qua tran Han Quoc vs Duc.\" title=\"\u0110T Mexico thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/DT-Mexico-thua-Thuy-Dien-Su-bat-an-cua-lich-su-ua-ve-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Mexico \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Mexico ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Mexico thua \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1eafc \u00c2u, C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189777.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c</span> gi\u00fap Mexico v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0nh 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Mexico ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Timo Werner</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Timo Werner l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018. Khi m\u00e0 Close \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f2n Mario Gomez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leipzig \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timo Werner gay that vong rat lon o World Cup 2018\" title=\"Timo Werner g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/so-9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Timo Werner g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. C\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng HLV Low \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Timo Werner \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u1ea7n sau 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c anh kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Timo Werner. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Miroslav Klose \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"679","checkdouble":"189862"},{"date":"17:20 28/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Senegal vs Colombia 21h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/truc-tiep-colombia-vs-senegal.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Colombia vs Senegal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Senegal vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 28/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1e