dng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 28/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ba-lan-vs-nhat-ban-463-189865.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP NH\u1eacT B\u1ea2N VS BA LAN</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"677","checkdouble":"189865"},{"date":"17:46 28/06","title":"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng? \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/anh-bi-tinh-nhuong-nhau-thang-dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n \u1edf World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n danh d\u1ef1, v\u00ec tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao v\u00e0 v\u00ec kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, h\u00e3y hy v\u1ecdng d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean s\u1ebd g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u201c\u0111\u1ebfm cua trong l\u1ed7\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng ch\u00e1y h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00eam nay.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eefng c\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1c trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 khi n\u00e0o? Argentina, 2002. \u0110\u1ee9c, 2001. H\u00e0 Lan, 1996. Ph\u00e1p, 1982. T\u00e2y Ban Nha, 1980 (kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m). Italia, 1977. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, 1966. Brazil, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd!</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Tam S\u01b0 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 4 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, n\u00f3i th\u1eadt l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i: Panama, Tunisia, Slovenia, Ecuador, Paraguay v\u00e0 Trinidad & Tobago. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng Costa Rica, Nigeria hay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Nhan-dinh-Anh-vs-Bi-Dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9: Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1edbn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf World Cup 2002</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng C\u0110V tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn th\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u00fd \u1ee9c v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Euro, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 chi m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u nhi\u1ec7m n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea1m qu\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au 52 n\u0103m ch\u01b0a v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o \u0111i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1i d\u1edbp 16 n\u0103m t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady th\u00ec, khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tdp.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb ngang c\u01a1 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, h\u00e3y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng m\u00e0 n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi, v\u00ec th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn, ch\u1ee9 xin \u0111\u1eebng tr\u1ed1n chui tr\u1ed1n l\u1ee7i l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-bi-1h00-ngay-296-noi-chien-premier-league-421-189801.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/Anh-vs-Bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-bi-1h00-ngay-296-noi-chien-premier-league-421-189801.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9 (1h00 ng\u00e0y 29/6): N\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Premier League</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018: Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec nh\u01b0ng v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee7 quan v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch quan, m\u00e0n n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Premier League n\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng \u00edt lu\u1ed3ng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ch\u00e2m ch\u01b0\u1edbc hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Anh thua B\u1ec9, hay ch\u00ed \u00edt c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau\u2026 l\u0129nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G. Ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110i s\u00e2u chi ti\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u1eefng Colombia, Senegal hay Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, v\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean xem ra, \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i h\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t khi b\u1eaft c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi 1/3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u1ea3 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1eeda \u1ea3i knock-out \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng G nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u201cth\u00fa d\u1eef\u201d Brazil trong khi b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee3i. C\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 v\u1ea1ch s\u1eb5n ra cho m\u00ecnh l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Anh-\u2013-Bi-tinh\u2026-nhuong-nhau-thang-Dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9: Nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng knock-out d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 logic nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, n\u01a1i logic \u0111\u00f4i khi ch\u1eb3ng mang ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec h\u1ebft. Trong khi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n theo ki\u1ec3u \u201c\u0111\u1ebfm cua trong l\u1ed7\u201d nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n d\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng hay ho g\u00ec r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-phai-chang-do-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-465-189805.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c</span>, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 H\u00e0 Lan, \u00dd v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ec3 thao, nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, th\u0103ng hoa tinh th\u1ea7n, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ea3m x\u00fac hay t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f5. Tho\u1ea1t nghe qua c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u00e1o r\u1ed7ng, s\u1ebfn s\u00faa trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng ng\u00e0y nay nh\u01b0ng qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, n\u00f3 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-421-189768.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-421-189768.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u201cdi\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gary Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eed h\u1ecfi xem th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p truy\u1ec1n g\u1eedi cho d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 g\u00ec n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng B\u1ec9, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn? <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m v\u1eady v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p h\u1ecd.\u201d \u2013 Y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u00e0 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i, c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 Brazil l\u00e0 \u00f4ng k\u1eb9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 trong m\u1eaft Tam S\u01b0. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n n\u00e0y hay sao?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau g\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e2u th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. T\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng s\u1ebd sinh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi sau c\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Anh-\u2013-Bi-tinh\u2026-nhuong-nhau-thang-Dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui!-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9: B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00f4ng gai h\u01a1n, Anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1eafng B\u1ec9, v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 khi ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, m\u1ecdi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1982 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00f3 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e1 hay b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00f4ng gai h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00eam nay, h\u00e0 c\u1edb g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1ed1n d\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 quen h\u01a1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u01a1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u1eady n\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn n\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac cho m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111anh th\u00e9p v\u00e0 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1edf h\u1ecd - s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 1982 chung \u0111\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Ph\u00e1p, Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc v\u00e0 Kuwait. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean m\u1eb7c cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out, 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 quan v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Anh-\u2013-Bi-tinh\u2026-nhuong-nhau-thang-Dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui!-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9: V\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh,ngay c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ghi nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn mang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1ee9 hai m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, khi d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eafn k\u1ebft hay b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1edbi x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1ee9 24 khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Euro 2016. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf thua m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng Argentina v\u00e0 Italia gi\u00e0 d\u01a1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb X\u1ee9 Wales gieo nh\u1ee5c \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Anh \u2013 B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh\u2026 nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng \u0110\u1eebng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/voi-tinh-yeu-bong-da-chang-co-dieu-gi-la-khong-the.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs B\u1ec9: Nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau th\u1eafng? Xin \u0111\u1eebng t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1ee9 hai b\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u201cx\u1ecbn\u201d \u0111\u00e2y? B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 hay tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung, t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u0169 b\u1ecf qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-bi-1h00-ngay-296-noi-chien-premier-league-421-189801.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs B\u1ec9</span> \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3 gian nan kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o t\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c th\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1eady xin h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eebng t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh con tin c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 may r\u1ee7i!</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/van-de-cua-tuyen-anh-vi-southgate-khong-phai-guardiola-421-189174.html\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh: V\u00ec Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-phai-chang-tuyen-duc-dang-tro-thanh-nhung-nguoi-anh-moi-421-189831.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia: Lukaku \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho m\u1ecdi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span>\u00a0</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"676","checkdouble":"189869"},{"date":"11:10 28/06","title":"Hitzlsperger: \"\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hitzlsperger-day-khong-phai-dt-duc-cua-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Thomas Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c \u00ea ch\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean t\u1edd Guardian, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c Hitzlsperger \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ch\u00ednh trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thua trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai &ndash; nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ed7ng khi vi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ch\u1edd m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y sinh l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1eady? Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m trong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi \u00c1o v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia. \u0110\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\" title=\"Mario Gomez c\u0169ng chung n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi \u0110\u1ee9c thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/14.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec Joachim Low lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea1i Nga. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Leroy Sane, sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Man City. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu m\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u1ebb trung, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i &ndash; t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Muller. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Joachim Low. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y &ndash; \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017-469-189802.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017-469-189802.html\">Hummels: \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017</span><br>\r\nMats Hummels cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"675","checkdouble":"189821"},{"date":"09:32 28/06","title":"Gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/gianh-ve-di-tiep-hlv-thuy-sy-van-cam-thay-khong-hai-long.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Costa Rica \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/HLV-Vladimir-Petkovic-noi-ve-tran-Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00f2a Costa Rica 2-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-thuy-sy-vs-costa-rica-421-189789.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</span> l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Vladimir Petkovic gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau 3 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E sau Brazil. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Petkovic th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Petkovic noi ve tran Thuy Sy vs Costa Rica\" title=\"HLV Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/gianh-ve-di-tiep-hlv-thuy-sy-van-cam-thay-khong-hai-long.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Schar b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, song Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"674","checkdouble":"189823"},{"date":"09:44 28/06","title":"HLV Oscar Ramirez: \"Costa Rica x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-martinez-noi-gi-truoc-tran-anh-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aleksandar Kolarov b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Serbia c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Brazil trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/aleksandar-kolarov-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-sau-tran-thua-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kolarov</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSerbia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. C\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Braizl vs Serbia</span> khi\u1ebfn Matic v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aleksandar Kolarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Serbia. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKolarov t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu ta thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n cho Man City. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Paulinho, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Kolarov tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi 4 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Serbia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, song Gary Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" title=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Serbia-vs-Brazil-Casemiro-tranh-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Brazil nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c Serbia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"673","checkdouble":"189824"},{"date":"09:50 28/06","title":"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/7_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap SLNA h\u1ea1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 56 \u0111\u1ebfn 66, </span>tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.</span> \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV T\u00e0i Em ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, n\u00ean d\u1eb7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 c\u1eadu ta. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay v\u00e0 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. C\u1eadu ta thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i h\u1ed3i x\u01b0a\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t may anh \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, SLNA l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/27/SLNA-3-2-Sai-Gon.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\">SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (KT): Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, CLB x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 H\u1ed3 Ph\u00fac T\u1ecbnh trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn SLNA c\u00f3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Qua \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"672","checkdouble":"189826"},{"date":"10:02 28/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 2-2 Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/thong-ke-an-tuong-tran-thuy-sy-22-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 Costa Rica c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n trong 5 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica - B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica - B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thong-ke-Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica---Bang-E-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa Rica may m\u1eafn c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 2-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Yann Sommer l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 ba ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, sau Noel Valladares n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 Andoni Zubizarreta n\u0103m 1998.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>2 &ndash; </strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-thuy-sy-vs-costa-rica-421-189789.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecdi b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E sau Brazil, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf&nbsp;v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>0 &ndash;</strong> L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 2006, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>32 &ndash;</strong> Trong s\u1ed1 32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, Costa Rica l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ghi b\u00e0n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia (0-1) v\u00e0 Brazil (0-2).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>24 &ndash;</strong> B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Costa Rica \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn sau 24 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Costa Rica co duoc 2 ban truoc Thuy Sy\" title=\"Costa Rica c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/095945-costa-rica.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa Rica c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>424 &ndash; </strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 424 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>6 - </strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 6/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>0 &ndash;</strong> Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>3 &ndash; </strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf 3 trong 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (1994, 2006 v\u00e0 2014), ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 n\u0103m 2010 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng&nbsp;b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"671","checkdouble":"189827"}]}